    "body": "Yes the goal of a PR for this issue is that adding the signature to the SMC as a field would allow **any** actor to handle incoming requests. Right now, only the proposer can do it as it is the only actor that can add the original signature back to the header. The goal of a PR for this would be to eliminate this constraint leveraging the work done in #196 @prestonvanloon.",
